 low enough for cosmic variance cancellation to be effective, i.e.~for large\nhalo number density and large $k_{\\rm max}$. This motivates exploring this\nregime observationally.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Feb 2018 18:55:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-20"}
