tainty in the retrieved albedo map, we\nrobustly identify a high albedo region (the Sahara desert) and a large\nlow-albedo region (the Pacific Ocean).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Feb 2018 19:00:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-19"}
